query:
SELECT work_id as "work_id!", work_name as "work_name!",
                          work_version as "work_version!", work_platform as "work_platform!",
                          instance_id as "instance_id!", row_num as "row_num!"
                   FROM instanceWork
                   WHERE work_platform ILIKE ('%' || $1 || '%')
                   ORDER BY row_num ASC
                   OFFSET $2
                   LIMIT $3
